{"title":"王泽源发奖金","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":125,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-4474","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>当然打台球只是王泽源的休闲娱乐活动，对待他的本职工作，他还是非常兢兢业业的。但是王泽源的老板是个张扒皮，每次都想克扣王泽源的工资和奖金，甚至制定出非常奇葩的规则。</p><p>又到了每年发年终奖的时候了，今年张老板的规则是这样的：给你n个数，每次你可以对任意一个数加1，直到所有的数都不相等为止，每加一次都要花费一定数额的费用。为了王泽源的幸福生活，聪明的你可否帮助王泽源，让他尽量少扣钱。</p><p><br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p><span style=\"\">第一行</span><span style=\"\">n</span><span style=\"\">，表示共有</span><span style=\"\">n</span><span style=\"\">个数。</span></p><p><span style=\"\">第二行共</span><span style=\"\">n</span><span style=\"\">个用空格隔开的非负整数</span><span style=\"\">ai</span><span style=\"\">。</span></p><p><br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(228, 240, 248);\">仅一个整数，表示加到让每个数都不相等的最少次数。</span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: monospace;\">4\n1 1 3 2</span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: monospace;\">3</span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p><br></p><p><span style=\"\">【样例说明】</span></p><p>让1+1+1+1 = 4，给定的数字变成4,1,3,2。</p><p><span style=\"\">【数据规模】</span></p><p>30%的数据，1&lt;=n&lt;=10</p><p>60%的数据，1&lt;=n&lt;=1000</p><p>80%的数据，1&lt;=n&lt;=30000，ai&lt;=1000，</p><p>100%的数据，1&lt;=n&lt;100000， ai&lt;=1000000。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}